Dialogue: 0,00:00:08.593,0:00:09.463,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Gunshot ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪♪ [ Alternative Rock:\N"Sea Lion" ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪♪ [ Ends ]
Dialogue: 0,00:00:46.813,00:00:50.773,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Addy,\Nyour dissertation\Nis entitled...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:51.464,00:00:54.008,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Analysis of Bone Trauma."
Dialogue: 0,00:00:54.347,00:00:57.613,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When viewed in cross section,\Nthe pressure and force...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.613,00:00:59.713,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exerted by the weapon\Ncan be assessed.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.833,00:01:03.073,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obtaining the cross section\Nwill compromise\Nthe original bone.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:03.403,00:01:06.072,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My technique preserves\Nbone surface morphology...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:06.103,00:01:08.203,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the use\Nof polyvinyl replication.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:08.353,00:01:11.443,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A transparent positive is made\Nby covering the impression...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:11.443,00:01:13.513,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with an aqueous solution\Nof synthetic polymer.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.573,00:01:16.332,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bones. Come on.\NWe got a body.\NWent up like a Roman candle.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.385,00:01:19.993,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Zack. How's it going?\N- So far, they don't like me.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:20.053,00:01:21.972,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shocker. Let's go.\N- [ Brennan ] I'm in\Nthe middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.782,00:01:26.085,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, real-life murder\Nand mutilation versus\Nacademic claptrap, no contest.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:26.994,00:01:29.860,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry. No offense.\N- This committee can carry on\Nwithout you, Dr. Brennan.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.213,00:01:32.443,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zack, just answer\Nthe questions.\N[ Booth ] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:33.973,00:01:35.143,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Booth ]\NOkay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:40.003,00:01:40.753,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next question?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:41.203,00:01:44.203,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect anyone\Nto take you seriously...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:44.203,00:01:46.363,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a working forensic\Nanthropologist...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.753,00:01:49.093,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you look\Nthe way you do?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.193,00:01:51.519,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:53.209,00:01:56.082,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Brennan ]\NMale, middle-aged.\NWhat was with Zack back there?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.293,00:01:59.108,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defending his dissertation.\NLast step before\Nhe gets his doctorate.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.712,00:02:02.383,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think these\Nare what's left\Nof his intestines.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.725,00:02:05.113,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna make it?\NNo. He's very dead.\N[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.253,00:02:09.013,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Zack.\NAh, 50-50.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.079,00:02:11.110,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stoolie.\NZack?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:11.173,00:02:13.243,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our victim.\NNo, he's a rat, a snitch.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.513,00:02:15.193,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?\NHis guts got spilled.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:15.193,00:02:17.982,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, spill your guts.\NVery literal.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:18.041,00:02:22.393,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hung up there like a scarecrow\Non a rooftop of a hotel used to\Nhouse witnesses. It's a warning.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.668,00:02:25.633,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something jammed\Ndown his trachea.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:26.233,00:02:29.833,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Zack ] I rectified their\Nerroneous assumptions concerning\Npolyvinyl replication.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.893,00:02:31.273,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You corrected them?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.533,00:02:33.553,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when they were wrong.\N[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.966,00:02:35.083,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the remains\Nready for X-ray?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.353,00:02:38.802,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Maybe\Nwe'll get lucky and I.D.\Nthe poor bastard that way.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:39.103,00:02:40.933,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we just got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.813,00:02:45.703,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My name is Garrett Delaney."
Dialogue: 0,00:02:46.813,00:02:48.193,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nmetallic here.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.213,00:02:54.643,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna turn out\Nto be some freaky, weird\Nritualistic thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.912,00:02:56.593,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.613,00:02:58.903,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christopher Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:00.163,00:03:02.170,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where's Dr. Brennan?\N- Her brother came for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:02.953,00:03:05.743,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad called you?\NYou're sure it was him?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.833,00:03:08.173,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You and your sister\Nare in danger," and he hung up.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:08.743,00:03:12.882,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spend half my time\Nwith a sniper-trained\NF.B.I. agent. I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:12.943,00:03:14.953,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempe, I know someone\Nis watching me.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:15.223,00:03:17.773,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your evidence?\NI can feel it\Non the back of my neck.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:18.493,00:03:20.683,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spend some time in jail,\Nyou develop a sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.467,00:03:27.103,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should stay\Nwith me for a few days.\NTempe, I have work.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.193,00:03:31.003,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I have Amy and the girls.\N- What about your sixth sense?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:31.243,00:03:31.483,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.233,00:03:34.393,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't not believe\Nin something one second,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.393,00:03:37.363,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then use it\Nagainst me in the next.\NIt's a long drive.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:37.453,00:03:39.793,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could start fresh tomorrow.\NAnd I've got...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:40.821,00:03:42.493,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cold beer in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:42.732,0:03:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink the Moroccan beer.\NTastes like ear wax.\NHow you doing, Russell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Booth.\NYou? Good?\NYeah. Good.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.418,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still make him nervous,\Ndon't I? Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always feel\Nlike you're abducting me?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.998,00:03:57.973,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Booth ]\NYeah. It turns out our corpse\Nis a former F.B.I. agent.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:58.333,00:04:01.182,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garrett Delaney,\Nhe left the F.B.I.\Nabout 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:01.183,00:04:04.093,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's now head of security of\Nsome big K Street lobbyist.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:05.113,00:04:06.943,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why'd he end up\Na human torch?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.243,00:04:08.532,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're here\Nto find out.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.433,00:04:12.973,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His place is much\Nbetter than yours.\NTen times better.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:13.153,00:04:14.923,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you\Nhe left public service.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.983,00:04:18.613,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes, uh,\Nmore money than I.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.903,00:04:21.193,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's all\Nyour dad said, huh?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.043,00:04:23.443,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is you're in danger?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:24.521,00:04:26.803,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And Russ's sixth sense agrees.\N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:27.883,00:04:30.823,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been practicing some\Nof the black ops stuff\Nyou taught me.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:31.051,00:04:31.722,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:32.592,00:04:35.052,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every F.B.I. agent\Nin the country is\Nlooking for my father.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.053,00:04:36.074,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's trying\Nto scare us off.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.346,00:04:38.532,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six months without\Na break in the case,\Nhe ain't gonna be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:38.533,00:04:40.601,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let me show you.\NMy dad's a career criminal.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.606,00:04:43.237,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because he says\Nthat Russ is in danger\Ndoesn't mean it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you\Nhow it's done, okay?\N[ Kicks Door ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. He might've\Ngotten it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Russ.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:59.428,00:05:02.653,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all pictures\Nof Russ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta Frank it up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frank it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frank it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.730,00:05:50.143,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect blend of\Nflavor and heat
Dialogue: 0,00:05:50.263,00:05:51.872,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put that $#!t on everything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[music playing]
Dialogue: 0,00:06:37.753,00:06:41.017,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you can give\Na gift like no other,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:41.623,00:06:44.503,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a gift that can help St.\NJude Children's Research
Dialogue: 0,00:06:44.533,00:06:46.273,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hospital save lives.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:47.023,00:06:49.093,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the\Nmost worthwhile place
Dialogue: 0,00:06:49.093,00:06:51.342,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to put your money when it\Ncomes to childhood cancer.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.913,00:06:53.472,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for St. Jude, I\Nwouldn't be sitting here today.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:54.612,00:06:57.133,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for St.\NJude, a lot of kids
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.282,00:06:58.930,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't be with their\Nfamilies every day.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:59.383,00:07:03.043,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come together to help\Nthe children of St. Jude fight
Dialogue: 0,00:07:03.073,00:07:04.213,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,childhood cancer.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:04.813,00:07:06.940,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit this website,\Ncall this number,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.123,00:07:11.048,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or scan the QR code with\Nyour $19 monthly donation.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:11.563,00:07:14.113,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join with your debit or\Ncredit card right now,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.233,00:07:17.533,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll send you this St.\NJude t-shirt you can proudly
Dialogue: 0,00:07:17.533,00:07:19.123,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wear to show your support.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.963,00:07:23.623,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you can help\NSt. Jude save lives.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.043,00:07:25.963,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a heart\Nfor somebody to say
Dialogue: 0,00:07:26.023,00:07:28.762,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this extra that I'm\Nwilling to give to St. Jude
Dialogue: 0,00:07:29.023,00:07:31.180,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that they can\Nhelp save more lives.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.543,00:07:35.857,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your monthly donation today\Nto help cure childhood cancer
Dialogue: 0,00:07:36.133,00:07:36.823,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[school bells]
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.335,00:08:41.257,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When pain says, “I'm here,”
Dialogue: 0,00:08:41.334,00:08:45.943,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say, “So are they.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,00:08:49.692,00:08:50.113,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALEVE
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.594,00:08:51.732,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who do you take it\Nfor?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.795,00:09:10.123,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready for whatever life\Nthrows your way.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.867,00:09:12.943,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Dial provides a\Nhard-working clean
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.033,00:09:15.733,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is gentle to skin with\Nits Skin Smart complex
Dialogue: 0,00:09:15.853,00:09:16.992,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 3 moisturizers
Dialogue: 0,00:09:17.203,00:09:19.573,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to leave your skin feeling\Nfresh and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:19.903,00:09:21.493,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing cleans like Dial.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.815,00:09:56.592,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me at work, me and Amy.\NThis was the day\Nbefore yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.652,00:09:58.257,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was right.\NSomebody's watching.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.366,00:10:00.943,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is worse than watching.\N- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:00.973,00:10:02.323,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is hunting.\N- Hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in kill.\NYou see these?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:05.958,00:10:09.499,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here. These are ranges.\NHe's picking out a spot\Nfrom which to shoot at you.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:10.185,00:10:13.458,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So what do I do now?\N- The hunter's dead.\NThe hunt is over, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:13.578,00:10:15.467,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else\Nknow you're here?\NOnly Amy.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:15.786,00:10:17.808,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Call Amy\Nand tell her if anyone\Ncalls looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,00:10:18.346,00:10:18.948,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't know\Nwhere you're at.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:21.268,00:10:24.498,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stay with me until\Nwe find out why Delaney\Nintended to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:25.019,00:10:27.108,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How are you gonna do that?\N- By figuring out\Nwho killed him.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.707,00:10:36.246,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Angela ]\NThis is the paper that was\Npulled from Delaney's throat.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:36.888,00:10:40.248,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was dated, signed,\Nand initialed at the bottom\Nof both sides of the page.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:41.658,00:10:43.158,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,February 1978.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:43.967,00:10:45.138,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like\Na cop's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:46.008,00:10:47.298,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense except,\N[ Typing ]
Dialogue: 0,00:10:48.528,00:10:53.418,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will not put an innocent man\Nin prison just because\Nhe is a political threat.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:53.778,00:10:55.697,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvin Beckett hasn't\Nbroken any law."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.\NMarvin Beckett?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:58.269,00:11:02.294,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the '60s, Marvin Beckett\Nwas a civil rights activist.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.302,00:11:03.768,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made his bones protesting...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.768,00:11:06.558,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,African American\Noverrepresentation\Nin the Vietnam War.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:06.678,00:11:10.038,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In '78, he was sent\Nto prison for life.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:10.577,00:11:12.199,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed an F.B.I. agent\Nnamed Gus Harper.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:12.768,00:11:16.098,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Augustus Harper?\NYeah. You know the case?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:17.088,00:11:20.238,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"August Harp."\NLook. Augustus Harper.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.408,00:11:21.768,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:22.368,00:11:24.468,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means Delaney's murder\Nhas something to do...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.468,00:11:26.088,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Marvin Beckett\Ngoing to prison.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:26.722,00:11:31.098,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, when you're good,\Nyou are very, very good.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:31.218,00:11:33.558,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1970s, Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:33.618,00:11:36.858,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a task force made up\Nof F.B.I., state police,\Nand local cops.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:37.038,00:11:40.188,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes bad. Starts taking a cut\Nfrom the same bank robbers\Nthey're supposed to be catching.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.729,00:11:44.027,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they conspire to plan\Na stack of stolen money\Non Marvin Beckett.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:44.808,00:11:46.578,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then this young agent,\Nright, Harper, okay?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:46.878,00:11:49.668,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He decides he can't live\Nwith that and decides\Nto blow the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:49.844,00:11:52.908,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read.\NThe same guy who's gonna blow\Nthe whistle on them...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:52.908,00:11:55.641,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for framing Marvin Beckett\Nthen gets murdered\Nby Marvin Beckett?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:55.641,00:11:57.467,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Talk about\Nkilling two birds\Nwith one stone.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:57.652,00:11:59.838,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else knows about this?\NUs and you. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:59.988,00:12:02.448,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep it that way.\NHey, I've seen this movie.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.748,00:12:05.140,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get killed\Non the way home.\NThen don't go home.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:06.768,00:12:07.518,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Chuckles ]\NYou serious?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.148,00:12:11.778,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty years ago,\NI was married to Gus Harper\Nfor exactly eight months.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:12.228,00:12:13.638,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure\NI can help you.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.363,00:12:16.128,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the contents\Nof the note?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.758,00:12:17.748,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you people want?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:18.798,00:12:19.998,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:21.496,00:12:24.078,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time the F.B.I.\Ncame to talk to me,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:24.438,00:12:26.357,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they told me to keep\Nmy mouth shut,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:26.838,00:12:28.998,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you won't get your\Nhusband's death benefits.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:29.330,00:12:31.818,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your husband is a good man.\NAnd he tried to do\Nthe right thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.818,00:12:35.118,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he ended up dead.\NI can't let that stand.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:36.523,00:12:43.548,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The F.B.I.\Nmurdered Gus.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:45.506,00:12:47.898,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they had\Na state funeral for him,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:48.558,00:12:51.618,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,complete with\Nthe grieving widow\Nas a centerpiece.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:52.848,00:12:56.028,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your husband's\Nhandwriting?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.768,00:13:00.738,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\NHe was compiling evidence.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.428,00:13:03.678,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was more?\NThere was a diary,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.798,00:13:06.198,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a dozen audiotapes,\Nfield notes.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:06.289,00:13:08.987,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And where did Gus keep it?\N- Safety-deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:09.438,00:13:11.897,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell us where\Nthat safety-deposit box was?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:12.468,00:13:21.198,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohio First Savings and Loan\Nin Dayton.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.198,00:13:21.707,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me one moment.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:27.072,00:13:29.772,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents robbed\Nthat exact bank...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:29.823,00:13:32.358,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just days after\NGus Harper was killed.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:33.417,00:13:36.198,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were looking\Nfor that evidence.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.678,00:13:39.018,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be why Delaney\Nwas stalking Russ.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:41.173,00:13:42.141,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.\NI have a few more questions\Nfor Barbara Harper, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,00:13:45.232,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go home and you be\Nwith your brother, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.986,00:13:53.838,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's Delaney?\N[ Zack ]\NDefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:54.558,00:13:56.987,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to keep working here\Nwhen I receive my doctorate.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:57.378,00:13:58.278,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd all like that.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.848,00:14:02.928,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she mean when she said,\N"How do you expect anyone\Nto take you seriously?"
Dialogue: 0,00:14:03.948,00:14:05.448,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a comment on...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:06.408,00:14:07.218,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your deportment.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:08.658,00:14:10.758,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Brennan doesn't\Ncare about deportment.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:12.108,00:14:12.558,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.128,00:14:17.298,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you work here,\Nyou won't be Brennan's\Ngrad student anymore.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:17.598,00:14:19.998,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a full-blown\Nforensic anthropologist.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:20.388,00:14:21.738,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cam will be your boss.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:22.128,00:14:24.618,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your opinion, does\Ndeportment matter to Cam?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:24.978,00:14:27.828,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say that Cam's not\Nthe kind of woman you catch...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:27.828,00:14:30.347,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with crusties\Nin the corner of her eye.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:34.608,00:14:36.588,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haley's six,\Nand Emma's eight.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:40.968,00:14:41.328,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempe?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:43.758,00:14:44.208,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:44.958,00:14:45.648,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:47.418,00:14:48.798,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempe, if I play\Nmy cards right,
Dialogue: 0,00:14:48.798,00:14:51.078,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these little girls\Nare gonna be your nieces\Nin the next couple months.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:51.078,00:14:52.578,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least you can do\Nis memorize their names.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:57.420,00:14:59.241,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're cute.\N- Haley has lung trouble.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:59.241,00:15:02.267,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to figure it out.\NYou ever deal with an H.M.O.?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:02.478,00:15:05.210,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's money, Russ,\NI can help.\NNo, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:06.288,00:15:08.868,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna become\Nthese little girls' daddy,\NI gotta man up for the job.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:09.888,00:15:11.538,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Knocking ]\NThat's not rational.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:11.970,00:15:13.578,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good mechanic.\NI'll take care of my own.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:15.108,00:15:17.918,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gus Harper's\Nservice history. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:18.228,00:15:20.208,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduated top half of his class\Nin Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:20.928,00:15:24.708,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was assigned to the Joint\NState-Federal Bank Robbery\NTask Force. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:24.977,00:15:29.238,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-The victim.\N-Back when he was Special Agent\NDelaney supervising Gus Harper.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:29.537,00:15:31.188,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy that was hunting me?\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:31.728,00:15:34.038,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here's a list\Nof the bank robbers\Nwith their F.B.I. code names.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:35.690,00:15:37.848,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Brennan ]\NDad's code name was Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:38.494,00:15:40.488,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Lewis, Clark,
Dialogue: 0,00:15:41.208,00:15:44.088,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magellan, Cook, Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.658,00:15:45.978,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All named after explorers.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.386,00:15:46.968,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.348,00:15:51.498,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Every one of these people\Nare deceased.\N- Except for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:51.738,00:15:54.469,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delaney was killed to send\Na message to the F.B.I.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:55.218,00:15:57.828,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Columbus coin was found\Nin the victim's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:58.908,00:16:01.248,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Columbus shot a man\Nin the head,
Dialogue: 0,00:16:01.788,00:16:03.108,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hung him from a pole,
Dialogue: 0,00:16:03.828,00:16:06.168,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gutted him,\Nand set him on fire.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:06.796,00:16:13.189,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Columbus is our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta Frank it up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frank it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frank it up!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.658,00:16:42.318,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.996,00:16:49.306,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect blend of\Nflavor and heat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put that $#!t on everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.448,00:16:58.638,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving\Nwithout these diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:58.728,00:16:59.268,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.658,00:17:00.798,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here for the stains.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.038,00:17:02.357,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Persil ProClean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOOM.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:03.888,00:17:04.757,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than Clean.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:04.759,00:17:06.138,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Persil ProClean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(inspiring music)
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.768,00:17:10.878,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate] I got my degree\Nat SNHU for my family.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:11.237,00:17:12.438,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate 1] This\Ndegree is for me.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:12.888,00:17:14.778,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate 2] I did\Nthis for my partner.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:15.410,00:17:16.247,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate 3] My siblings.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:16.908,00:17:17.898,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate 4] My daughter.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.648,00:17:19.126,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Graduate 5] My son.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:19.608,00:17:20.868,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations, dad.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:20.881,00:17:22.338,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:22.578,00:17:24.375,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [Announcer] No matter who\Nyou get your degree for,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:24.558,00:17:27.108,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Southern New Hampshire\NUniversity can help\Nyou get it done.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:27.438,00:17:30.947,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With low online tuition and\Nmultiple term starts per year.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:31.158,00:17:33.498,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the best time to get\Nstarted is right now.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:34.068,00:17:35.958,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit snhu.edu.
