Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.55,0:55:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I'd make a deal with God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.49,0:55:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ And get him to swap\Nour places ♪
