Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.57,0:56:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ And get him to swap\Nour places ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.74,0:56:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Be running up that road
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.25,0:56:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Be running up that hill
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.75,0:56:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ With no problem ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.55,0:56:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NZack's doctorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.46,0:56:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to recommend him\Nfor a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.46,0:56:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put him in front\Nof a jury. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.33,0:56:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put in a good word\Nin Pure Research. That way, he\Ncan come visit once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.83,0:56:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Visit?\N- Dr. Saroyan,\NDr. Brennan, Dr. Hodgins,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.44,0:56:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to present\Nyour colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.64,0:56:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Zachary\NUriah Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.44,0:56:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Chuckles ]\NLook at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.05,0:56:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All grown up.\N[ Saroyan ]\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.08,0:56:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.52,0:57:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can learn how to be effective\Nin front of juries.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.99,0:57:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zack can learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.16,0:57:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, he's hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.47,0:57:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I\Nto break up this team?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.54,0:57:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is on me, Dr. Addy.\NAnywhere you want to go.\NThe diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.01,0:57:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere, I said.\NI like the diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.71,0:57:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do me a favor,\NUriah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.11,0:57:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need a little time\Nto adjust to\Nyour fascist haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.05,0:57:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.22,0:57:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations,\NDr. Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.30,0:57:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dr. Brennan.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.03,0:57:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Angela ]\NZack, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.57,0:57:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Hodgins ]\NCongratulations.\NHear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.17,0:57:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Hodgins ]\NIt's about time, man.\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.77,0:57:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Saroyan ]\NYou should be proud\Nof yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.88,0:58:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.15,0:58:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the attorney general took\None look at the, uh, evidence\Nyour father provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.75,0:58:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, you know,\Nhe reinstated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.19,0:58:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.09,0:58:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. We, uh, found\Nanother burned body.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.79,0:58:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same place, same setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.96,0:58:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirby?\NI'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.23,0:58:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kirby's blood\Nin your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.70,0:58:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's still trying\Nto warn people.\NLeave me and Russ alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.81,0:58:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Russ, he's safe\Nwith your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.48,0:58:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're warning people\Nto stay away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.95,0:58:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?\NI'm sorry that you had\Nto go through it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.45,0:58:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching your family drive off,\Nyou know, leaving you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.19,0:58:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NMy father is-- is--
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.22,0:58:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your dad.\NAnd he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.47,0:58:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm just--
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.70,0:58:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just one of those people who\Ndoesn't get to be in a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.94,0:59:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.01,0:59:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Bones.\NHey, there's more\Nthan one kind of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.55,0:59:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Zack got the job, right?\NCome in and\Ncongratulate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.56,0:59:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. These are your squints.\NNot my squints.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.89,0:59:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Booth, we are\Nall of us your squints.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.63,0:59:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favor and pat\NZack on the shoulder\Nwith an open hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.10,0:59:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why? Does that\Nmean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.54,0:59:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Chuckles ]

